{"tid":241083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[提醒巴打]今日係紅十字會賣旗日","createTime":"2017-05-13T00:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T01:46:16.000Z","uid":30453,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48978cbd07e2504f28084281bc0734c988d3dcc7","tid":241083,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我呼籲大家千其唔好買</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港紅十字會賣旗日<br />\n日期：2017年5月13日（ 星期六） <br />\n時間：上午7時至中午12時15分<br />\n<br />\n特別係不讓座 、不捐血、不買旗嘅巴打唔好見到學生妹就忍唔住去買<br />\n行政費用同埋紅十字最近啲野大家都知<br />\n最好就全部機構都唔買<br />\n但如果你係佢死忠一定要買我都吹得你漲<br />\n順便投埋票<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔買<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買"},{"pid":"d6a9a7f7325f562b61196c20fd355a43b4e21bf1","tid":241083,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T00:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b3c08c537a5e33d085e0b46a097c6f671d5e3f","tid":241083,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T00:53:23.000Z","msg":"買旗 不了"},{"pid":"12bf932223286eeb28f3a702e736cb1f14fc8f5c","tid":241083,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302aa7ab1c8a55b0a202a79d04bd1519c857e3cc","tid":241083,"uid":39225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買旗 不了</blockquote>"}]}